Included functions: car launcher, widgets, a set of stylish large speedometers, support of system widgets, music player with visualization and search, the ability to select the logo of your car, set your own background image, recording and viewing of geographic tracks, full screen mode, built-in widgets, metering speed and acceleration, display speed graphic and a lot of other useful features.

The program is designed to work in the car radio system with the android, but you can install it on your smartphone or tablet.

Version 3 is even better and more convenient. Added import and export of desktops, icon generator, split screen support, vertical screen support and several new themes.

Popular questions (see more questions in the internal help file):
1) Long click for Play button - choose system player.
2) Supported music formats: mp3, ogg, flac, m4a;
3) Supported navigation: Google maps, Yandex Navigator and other (see internal help file)
4) Long click on any button for customization (action, icon, command)
5) Auto applications are not visible (go to Apps - use long click / Explore function).
6) Can I replace car image? Yes, see help file for more info.

For 8227L devices: You need to disable internal CWG Player, unset Record Audio permissions and use external player for better perfomance. The system in such radio tape recorders is not complete and there are problems with interception of audio focus.
descriptionShort: Car launcher with themes, widgets, music control, gps tracker, and customization
